OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 31 Jul to Fri 14 Aug
OL,6,FPerhaps a somewhat more changeable
OL,7,Fperiod, with the potential for showers
OL,8,For thunderstorms or even some longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain at times, these most
OL,10,Flikely to the north. Drier and
OL,11,Fbrighter interludes are also likely,
OL,12,Fperhaps more likely across the south
OL,13,Fand southeast. Temperatures are likely
OL,14,Fto be above normal with some hot
OL,15,Fspells possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
